					<p class="card-text smText contentFont">The main objective of Superklok Labs is to provide high-grade service in all areas of cloud computing consultation. Full-stack app design is carried out using the MongoDB, Express, React, Node stack. Legacy app containerization is accomplished using Docker and container orchestration specialization is with Kubernetes.</p>
