					<p class="card-text smText contentFont">Front-end web design specializing in React and harnessing the full power of CSS flexbox in order to create responsive custom websites. Contact <a href="mailto:sales@superklok.com">sales@superklok.com</a> to book a consultation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row my-lg-3">
		<div class="col-lg-6 mb-3 mb-lg-0">
			<div class="card shadow whiteBG">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h5 class="card-title mdText contentFont pt-2 ms-3">French Translation</h5>
